property_sql_factory_datasets.sql:
SELECT 
    'EnterVendorInvoice' || '::' || "VendorInvoice"."ID"         AS "ID",
    "VendorInvoice"."ID"                                         AS "VendorInvoice",
    "VendorInvoice"."CreationTime"                               AS "Time",
    "VendorInvoice"."User_ID"                                    AS "ExecutedBy",
    "VendorInvoice"."CreationExecutionType"                      AS "ExecutionType",
    "VendorInvoice"."InvoiceCategory"                            AS "InvoiceCategory"
FROM "o_custom_VendorInvoice" AS "VendorInvoice"
WHERE "VendorInvoice"."CreationTime" IS NOT NULL

sql_factory_datasets.sql:
SELECT DISTINCT 
    "Event"."ID"                     AS "ID",
    "Object"."ID"                    AS "PurchaseDocumentLine"
FROM "e_custom_EnterVendorInvoice" AS "Event"
    LEFT JOIN "o_custom_VendorInvoice" AS "VendorInvoice"
        ON "Event"."VendorInvoice_ID" = "VendorInvoice"."ID"
    LEFT JOIN "o_custom_VendorInvoiceLine" AS "VendorInvoiceLine"
        ON "VendorInvoice"."ID" = "VendorInvoiceLine"."VendorInvoice_ID"
    LEFT JOIN "o_custom_PurchaseDocumentLine" AS "Object"
        ON "VendorInvoiceLine"."PurchaseDocumentLine_ID" = "Object"."ID"
WHERE "Object"."ID" IS NOT NULL
